An online code playground with stdin/stdout/stderr support.

To run locally:

> node index.js

To deploy it online (it's recommended to use Heroku), you
should build a Docker image for it:

> docker build -t <your-name>/<project-name> .
> heroku container:login
> heroku create <app-name>
> heroku container:push web --app <app-name>
> heroku container:release web --app <app-name>

In case you don't want to build Docker locally, you can do it on Heroku
with the help of heroku.yml:

> heroku create <app-name>
> heroku stack:set container

